            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avius</ex></expan> Felicio <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustalis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>col</abbr><ex>oniae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aq</abbr><ex>uincensium</ex></expan> vi<lb break="no" n="2"/>vos <note>sic</note> sibi et Flaviae Secun<lb break="no" n="3"/>dinae <expan><abbr>quond</abbr><ex>am</ex></expan> conlibertae <lb n="4"/>et uxori quae vixit <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>nos</ex></expan> LV et <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>ito</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avio</ex></expan> Felicissimo <expan><abbr>quond</abbr><ex>am</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>filio naturali qui <expan><abbr>vixi</abbr><ex>t</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>os</ex></expan> XXIII et <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>ito</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avio</ex></expan> Ingenuo <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>fil</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> legitimo et <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>ito</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avio</ex></expan> Felici <lb n="9"/><expan><abbr>fil</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan> naturali et Flaviae <lb n="10"/>Feliculae filiae naturali <lb n="11"/>et Flaviae Felicissimae nepti <lb n="12"/>vivis <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avius</ex></expan> Felicio <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>upra</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>criptis</ex></expan> et sibi <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>aciendum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>uravit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Gefunden in Wiederverwendung für ein spätantikes Grab. Von der ursprünglichen Verwendung sind auf der jetzigen Rückseite noch Reste der Darstellung eines Mannes und eines Hundes, darunter von verschiedenen Werkzeugen erhalten. Auf der jetzigen Vorderseite oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes Reste einer Reliefdarstellung des Aktaion(?); die Buchstaben D und M der Z. 1 befinden sich auf den Pilastern zu Seiten des Inschriftfeldes. (B): Nagy, AE 1939: Z. 7: vix(it).</p>
            </div>
